User case: exchange message
actor: user
pre_condition: 
      the sender and receiver are existing user of CircleRound
      the user is currently watching a thread or have received a message
trigger: the user reply to a thread or a message
Event Flow:
1. the user reply to a thread or a message
2. the system save the message into database, and push to the recepient 
3. recepient can either delete the message or reply back
4. if reply back, go back to step 1
